      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must hold ISO 9001 certification and maintain full version-controlled test suite with traceability to requirements at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has partial version control and unit testing but lacks formal ISO 9001 certification. Achieved level 2 falls below required level 4 for MRL 5 VAD application."
    },
    {
