      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical flows must demonstrate expected convergence rates; manufactured solution verification required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index computed on pipe flow benchmark; manufactured solution verification not performed. Convergence rate confirmed only for velocity, not for hemolysis scalar transport."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent must bound discretization error to within 5% of QoI at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed; GCI for hemolysis index is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 is one step below required level 4."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
