      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenarios must span the intended VAD operating envelope; interpolation and extrapolation risk must be explicitly bounded.",
      "rationale": "Validation conducted only at nominal design point (5 L/min, 2500 RPM). Off-design conditions representing pathological VAD states not included; extrapolation risk unquantified."
