      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for choice of turbulence model and hemolysis power-law exponent must be provided with sensitivity analysis; alternative model forms must be compared.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected without comparative assessment against LES or DNS reference data for rotating blood pump geometry. Hemolysis power-law constants from Giersiepen not validated for this pump class."
