      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Monte Carlo or equivalent UQ must propagate uncertainty in blood rheology, inlet flow waveform, and wall compliance through to hemolysis QoI with full sensitivity ranking.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed over viscosity and inlet velocity; wall compliance and hematocrit-dependent rheology excluded. Sensitivity ranking incomplete; 95th-percentile hemolysis estimate not reported."
