      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size must be statistically justified; inter-sample variability in haemolysis measurements must be characterised.",
      "rationale": "Three experimental replicates used; no power analysis performed. Inter-sample coefficient of variation for NIH not reported. Sample size insufficient to characterise biological variability at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
