      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstration that simulation input parameters (geometry, boundary conditions, fluid properties) are equivalent to experimental conditions within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Pump geometry sourced from FDA benchmark STL file; as-manufactured tolerances of physical test article not compared. Fluid property equivalency between bovine and human blood not established."
